Name: West End Alexandria
Comment: KAB7046 near Alexandria, (independent) County, Virginia OPEN Repeater is open access using PL Code 141.3 Hz (4A) only. All other PL Codes are private. Repeater antenna is a 10dB 7 Element Celwave PD688S pointed 050 degrees from site into Washington, DC. Coverage up to 18 miles NE and 5 miles on sides and back of beam (yagi).

Name: WSDH649
Comment: WSDH649 near Stafford, Stafford County, Virginia OPEN 2 x Motorola CDM 1250, IDOM4 controller, XLT duplexer, Comet CA-712EFC 9.0dbi GMRS 10 ft. vertical antenna atop 25ft DXE-TFK25 mast.    Long term plans include high availability power. I do have battery backup and a generator onsite. However, the capacity of battery is small and manual generator transfer is required.    I intend to increase the battery storage and build a charge control/power distribution system to allow solar and dual fuel gas/lng generator source.
